text: Huron is a city in the eastern part of South Dakota, United States. It is the county seat of Beadle County, and 14,263 people lived there at the 2020 census. Huron became a city in 1883. == References == == Other websites == *City of Huron website Category:County seats in South Dakota Category:Cities in South Dakota Category:1883 establishments in Dakota Territory
title: Huron, South Dakota
